To prove a point?

17:08.569 --> 17:10.401
At first, but then
something magical happen--

17:10.695 --> 17:12.060
No, that's why
| brought you here.

17:12.365 --> 17:13.320
Oh, my God.

17:13.616 --> 17:14.856
Penny, let me handle this.

17:15.159 --> 17:16.944
